    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Celestial courtesans, beautiful female beings in Hindu and Buddhist religion. Often depicted as ethereal, flying, or cloud-borne female deities; for example, they may be depicted scattering flowers above preaching scenes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
